oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Cedarcrest Jamboree - 1949-05-21 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM's Cedarcrest Jamboree, originally broadcast 1949-05-21, part 2. Hosted by Louie Buck and Cowboy Copas, with Lazy Jim Day, the Oklahoma Cowboys, Little Jimmy Dickens, and Red Herron. Sponsored by Cedarcrest shoes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Lazy Jim Day; Oklahoma Cowboys; Little Jimmy Dickens; Cowboy Copas; Red Herron
